data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
This application allows you to easily modify RDP settings in the Windows Registry without having to remember the key locations.
Admin priveledges are required to modify HKLM, for the RDP Port.
Visit my website by clicking the button below for more utilities.
License: GNU General Public License v3. Source code available on my website, and GitHub
- For Reference - MRU Location: HKEY_CURRENT_USER\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Terminal Server Client\Default History Location: HKEY_CURRENT_USER\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Terminal Server Client\Servers Port #: HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\System\CurrentControlSet\Control\Terminal Server\WinStations\RDP-Tcp\PortNumber
George Babichev 2016
